title: Elon Musk Says Twitter 'Will, In Fact, Be OK Next Year'
description: The billionaire CEO said the social-media company he recently acquired was on track to log $3 billion in negative free-cash flow before his cost cuts.

title: The End of Netflix Password Sharing Is Nigh
description: More than 100 million viewers use borrowed passwords to watch content on the streaming giant. Putting a stop to the practice without alienating customers will be a challenge.

title: ChatGPT Wrote My AP English Essay. I Passed.
description: OpenAI’s new chatbot can write essays on complex topics. Our columnist went back to high school AP Literature to see how good those essays are.

title: Cybersecurity Firms Cut Staff as Fears About Economy, Funding Mount
description: The wave of layoffs started this summer and has spanned departments, including workers in technical roles.

title: NFL in Advanced Talks With Google's YouTube for 'Sunday Ticket' Rights Deal
description: The subscription-only package allows football fans to watch most Sunday afternoon games.
